data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. *MARKET-DRIVIN PRICE IMPROVEMENT* Are you ready to live in a highly desirable area in a gorgeous  4 bedroom house?  Open the front door and enter an arched foyer with a full view into the extremely spacious great room with an enjoyable view out to the pool.  Relax in an oversized master bedroom with a large master bath, updated with glass sinks and a spacious walk-in shower.  The kitchen is a dream with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and plenty of room for a breakfast nook.  It opens into a large dining room with an impressive working fireplace that affords a relaxing view out to the stunning enclosed pool area, fenced for privacy.  It has a double car garage with plenty of room to park your cars and toys.  The indoor laundry room is a great benefit when you live in Florida! This is a house that will make you a very proud homeowner, ready to make the memories of a lifetime!
